node.text: Bronte you are the sweetest!! Katie, are you kidding?!! Perfection, as always! ✨✨✨
Actually insane, no words. Thank you so much Katie. Beyond ❤️
I love these !!! So natural 😍 I’d love to have you here on our Estate one day 😍
@jopanckridge you’re so welcome, it was a pleasure meeting you all! And your house is divine!

Unbelievable photos Katie. Just so beautiful. Can’t believe how stunning my girl and her man look. The House looks pretty good too!!
Thank you for making Brontë and Michael’s day so special.
Oh these are just absolutely gorgeous!! Well done 😍 @brontepanckridge you are a stunner 🔥
